These definitely are worried. And then someone said it looks like a tremendous amount of learning

00:19:13.839 --> 00:19:19.359
and work. How long did it take for the results, for you to get the results that you presented today?

00:19:21.280 --> 00:19:25.599
That's really kind of like seven years worth. Oh, wow. Okay. Seven or eight years worth.

